@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

left to right direction
hide circle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

title Ticket Service ERM (PostgreSQL)

entity "tickets" as tickets {
  *id : uuid <<PK>>
  --
  ticket_type : int
  email : varchar(255)
  status : int
  created_at : timestamptz
  data : jsonb
}

note right of tickets
ticket_type:
- 1 = Client
- 2 = Partner
- 3 = PartnerCar

status:
- 1 = Pending
- 2 = Approved
- 3 = Rejected
end note

note bottom of tickets
data JSONB stores polymorphic payloads:
- client ticket fields
- partner ticket fields
- partner-car ticket fields

Logical external references inside JSON:
- reviewedByManagerId -> identity-service.users.id
- relatedPartnerUserId -> identity-service.users.id
- file names -> file-service objects
- car image ids / urls -> image-service objects
end note

@enduml
